<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a3440b2-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s4018"><num value="4018">§ 4018.</num><heading> Annual reports</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Every person to whom a certificate of review is issued shall submit to the Secretary an annual report, in such form and at such time as the Secretary may require, that updates where necessary the information required by <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s4012/a">section 4012(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a3440b3-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/290/tIII/s308">Pub. L. 97–290, title III, § 308</ref>, <date date="1982-10-08">Oct. 8, 1982</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/1244">96 Stat. 1244</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7a3440b4-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id7a3440b5-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id7a3440b6-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1982-10-08">Oct. 8, 1982</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/97/290/s312">section 312 of Pub. L. 97–290</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s4011">section 4011 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
